Class AdversarialSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • code.AdversarialSearch.AdversarialSearch
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlphaBeta, MiniMax

    public abstract class AdversarialSearch
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class that all search algorithms (meaning alphabeta and minimax) inherit from.
